ps://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A1t-%C4%90%C3%B4-L%E1%BA%A1t/author-o6P2TdkwVUJwiHY0ASq8kw">Tát Đô Lạt</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-%C4%90%C3%A0o/poem-QDLsHB0eRYr_a4LJ2gkNPA">Tặng Tiết Đào - 贈薛濤</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/Thanh-tr%E1%BB%A7ng/poem-tMZS9w4MVru3V1c1Uk-YLQ">Thanh trủng - 青塚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-H%E1%BA%A1/Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C3%A2m-h%C3%A0nh/poem-2cIzwGrRwoKxNBGrGBCfJg">Thương tâm hành - 傷心行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-H%E1%BA%A1/author-6YXs2qoM-0pPFaxDDrLTew">Lý Hạ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
